      "content": "- **User Authentication**: Allows users to securely log in and manage their personal accounts.\n- **View Dashboard Summaries**: Displays an overview of financial status, including key metrics and AI-generated insights.\n- **Track Income and Expenses**: Enables users to record and categorize all incoming and outgoing financial transactions.\n- **Set Financial Goals**: Allows users to define and monitor progress towards their savings and financial objectives.\n- **Receive Investment Suggestions**: Provides beginner-friendly recommendations for investment opportunities.\n- **View Financial Alerts**: Notifies users about important financial events or potential issues.\n- **Generate Financial Reports**: Creates detailed reports on spending, income, and goal progress.\n- **View Interactive Charts**: Visualizes financial data through dynamic charts and graphs.\n- **AI-Powered Financial Advice**: Offers personalized financial guidance and tips based on user data.\n- **Auto-Categorize Expenses**: Automatically assigns categories to recorded expenses for easier tracking.\n- **Answer Finance Questions**: Provides simple, clear answers to user queries about personal finance.",
